# ðŸ§® Flask Day 3 â€” Display Data in Tables

---

## **Goal**

Display fetched data inside HTML tables using **Jinja2 loops**.

Example:

```html
<table class="table table-striped">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>ID</th>
            <th>Product Name</th>
            <th>Price</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        {% for product in products %}
        <tr>
            <td>{{ product.id }}</td>
            <td>{{ product.name }}</td>
            <td>{{ product.price }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>
```

---

## ðŸ§  Task 3

